trans-unit.source: Releases the resources used by the <xref href="System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigir ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>.
trans-unit.target: Kall avhending når du er ferdig med <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Fjerningsmetoden forlater den <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter å avhending, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>ble bruker.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase> </xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: **Note** Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>.
trans-unit.target: **Obs** alltid kall fjerne før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker vil ikke bli frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase"> </xref> og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()` method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av offentlig `Dispose()` metoden og <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`Aktiverer den beskyttede `Dispose(Boolean)` metoden med den `disposing` parameteren satt til `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>aktiverer `Dispose` med `disposing` satt til `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is true, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase> references.
trans-unit.target: Når den `disposing` -parameteren er SANN, denne metoden Frigjør alle ressurser holdes av administrerte objekter som denne <xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>referanser.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AttachmentBase>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden starter den `Dispose()` metode for hver referert objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.
